      <title>俄罗斯黑客试图在选举前欺骗德国政客</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-22/russian-hackers-tried-duping-german-politicians-before-elections</link>
      <description><![CDATA[根据 Mandiant 的最新研究，俄罗斯间谍发起了一场针对德国政党的黑客活动，试图用虚假的晚宴邀请来欺骗他们。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-22/russian-hackers-tried-duping-german-politicians-before-elections</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 22 Mar 2024 16:44:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>众议院在政府关门截止日期前几小时通过了 1.2 万亿美元法案</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-22/house-passes-1-2-trillion-bill-hours-before-shutdown-deadline</link>
      <description><![CDATA[众议院在周五午夜部分政府关闭最后期限前几小时通过了一项 1.2 万亿美元的政府拨款法案，拒绝了保守派大幅削减国内支出的要求。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-22/house-passes-1-2-trillion-bill-hours-before-shutdown-deadline</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 22 Mar 2024 15:46:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
